episodes.title: Charles Manson - Inside Charles Manson's Crazed Cult
episodes.description: Charles Milles Manson was born on November 12, 1934, in Cincinnati, Ohio. From the beginning, Manson's life seemed destined for chaos and marginalization. His mother, Kathleen Maddox, was only 16 years old when she gave birth, and Manson's father, Colonel Walker Scott, never officially acknowledged him.
